  • PROPPERTEE REALTORS

    “Real estate cannot be lost or stolen, nor can it be carried away. Purchased with common sense, paid for in full, and managed with reasonable care, it is about the safest investment in the world.” - Franklin D. Roosevelt

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row equal_height=”yes” css=”.vc_custom_1600594482056{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;}”][vc_column css=”.vc_custom_1606712168003{background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}”][g5plus_space desktop=”10″ tablet=”10″ tablet_portrait=”10″ mobile_landscape=”10″ mobile=”10″][g5plus_space desktop=”10″ tablet=”10″ tablet_portrait=”10″ mobile_landscape=”10″ mobile=”10″][vc_row_inner content_placement=”middle”][vc_column_inner width=”1/2″][vc_single_image image=”6515″ img_size=”full”][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=”1/2″][vc_empty_space][g5plus_heading sub_title=”About Us” title=”PROPPERTEE REALTORS” el_class=”mg-bottom-35″][vc_column_text]PROPPERTEE REALTORS started its working from 2018 with a face book page, just to promote its initial name and some builder’s projects to generate leads and queries; soon we started as a start up and become one of the fastest growing companies in Real Estate Sector. We mainly deal in NCR region, in residential, commercial and leasing. We have a good base of our clients and so as the properties according to their requirements. Our operations are in EAST DELHI, NOIDA, GREATER NOIDA, NOIDA EXPRESSWAY, YEIDA, NOIDA EXTENSION AND SECTOR-150, Along with that we are also expending it to MUMBAI and PUNE soon. Our motto is to make property buying reliable and comfortable to our clients.[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]We as PROPPERTEE REALTORS are truly and faithfully committed to our commitments and words to always provide our clients and customers the best knowledge and services, according to their needs we as professionals also provide with our best portfolio management team with their 10 years of experience. We are also committed to the well-being and fair treatment of the public, as well as our professionals.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_empty_space][vc_column_text]We strongly believes that in BUSINESS “U” comes first and “I” later so just by this theory our clients(you) are more important to us, as in this service industry we provide maximum paper work and documentations related services at the door steps by our professionals, we have an experienced trained team of legal lawyers who cross check each documents closely before every deal[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=”stretch_row” css=”.vc_custom_1595570590789{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #f8f8f8 !important;}”][vc_column][g5plus_heading sub_title=”TYPES OF” title=”REAL ESTATE” text_align=”text-center”][vc_empty_space height=”20px”][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=”1/3″][g5plus_heading layout_style=”style2″ title=”Residential” css=”.vc_custom_1595569075336{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}”][vc_column_text]Residential includes both new construction and under construction homes. The most common category is nuclear-family homes. There are also flats, plots, penthouses, duplexes, triple-deckers, villas, farmhouses, Kotahi, bungalows and vacation homes.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=”1/3″][g5plus_heading layout_style=”style2″ title=”Commercial” css=”.vc_custom_1595570194668{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}”][vc_column_text]Commercial includes shopping centers and malls, medical and educational buildings, hotels and offices. Apartment buildings are often considered commercial, even though they are used for residences as serviced apartments. That’s because they are owned to produce income.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=”1/3″][g5plus_heading layout_style=”style2″ title=”Industrial” css=”.vc_custom_1595570388941{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}”][vc_column_text]Industrial includes manufacturing buildings and property, as well as warehouses. The buildings can be used for research, production, storage, and distribution of goods. Some buildings that distribute goods are considered commercial real estate.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width=”1/2″][g5plus_heading layout_style=”style2″ title=”Land” css=”.vc_custom_1595570455549{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}”][vc_column_text]Land includes vacant land, working farms, and ranches. The subcategories within vacant land include undeveloped, early development or reuse, subdivision and site assembly.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=”1/2″][g5plus_heading layout_style=”style2″ title=”Leasing” css=”.vc_custom_1595570522276{padding-top: 20px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}”][vc_column_text]Leasing includes renting of offices/shops/residential and retaining the best tenants with a compelling leasing and marketing strategy. Negotiate the most advantageous lease terms to secure maximum occupancy and value.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=”stretch_row” disable_element=”yes” css=”.vc_custom_1595568012877{padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #f8f8f8 !important;}”][vc_column offset=”vc_col-md-6″][g5plus_space desktop=”0″ tablet=”0″ tablet_portrait=”30″ mobile_landscape=”30″ mobile=”30″]

Our vision is to become a dynamic real estate consultant of India that we make property buying and selling as simple as we can by full commitment to its customers. To provide accurate and up-to-date information, skilled analysis and the most sound Real Estate advice. To continually explore new ideas and technology, to make selling and buying of Real Estate faster, less costly and easier. Our motto is our client’s growth also winning the hearts by fulfilling their dreams.

[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=”stretch_row” css=”.vc_custom_1595400994310{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}” el_class=”overflow-inherit”][vc_column][g5plus_heading sub_title=”WHY NAME” title=”PROPPERTEE?” text_align=”text-center” el_class=”mg-bottom-35″][vc_column_text]

 Yes we misspell and it’s all because we wanted to make our name attractive and catchy with a message that defines our vision and the motto as well.

[/vc_column_text][vc_row_inner equal_height=”yes” content_placement=”middle” gap=”15″][vc_column_inner width=”1/2″ css=”.vc_custom_1595400624346{background-image: url(https://proppertee.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/brian-babb-256298-unsplash.png?id=3356) !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}”][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=”1/2″][g5plus_heading layout_style=”style2″ title=”Second P” css=”.vc_custom_1595567789155{padding-top: 10px !important;padding-bottom: 10px !important;}”][vc_column_text]Is for practicality as we believe in being practical not virtual[/vc_column_text][g5plus_heading layout_style=”style2″ title=”T-Tangible” css=”.vc_custom_1595400829367{padding-top: 10px !important;padding-bottom: 10px !important;}”][vc_column_text]It’s being touchable or real something that can be understood and scientific that is not disputed. What we are and what developer’s we work with are equally reliable and verified as thoroughly with all the facts.[/vc_column_text][g5plus_heading layout_style=”style2″ title=”E-Economical” css=”.vc_custom_1595400842201{padding-top: 10px !important;padding-bottom: 10px !important;}”][vc_column_text]It’s saving use of resources. Economical implies prudent planning in the disposition of resources so as to avoid unnecessary waste or expense, we know the value of home and thus we understand and make it more economical & budgeted you our clients.[/vc_column_text][g5plus_heading layout_style=”style2″ title=”E-Eternity” css=”.vc_custom_1595400860736{padding-top: 10px !important;padding-bottom: 10px !important;}”][vc_column_text]”Time Without End, or Infinity,” like no other we promise to reach and solve all your property related FAQ’S, thus we aren’t planning to ever split up once we are connected to our clients we make sure we be with them till the time they get possession and all paperwork done by the developers end and so as for future.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=”stretch_row” css=”.vc_custom_1595325341957{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-position: center !important;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}” el_class=”overflow-inherit”][vc_column][g5plus_heading sub_title=”WE ALSO” title=”DO COMPLETE” text_align=”text-center” el_class=”mg-bottom-35″][vc_row_inner equal_height=”yes” content_placement=”middle” gap=”20″][vc_column_inner width=”1/2″ css=”.vc_custom_1595327375457{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-right: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;padding-left: 40px !important;background-color: #002c5b !important;}”][vc_column_text] Property analysis
